AN ACT
To repeal sections 67.799, 67.1551, 68.250, 71.800, 115.123, 137.016, 137.055, 137.073,
137.079, 137.082, 137.115, 137.1040, 137.1050, 137.1055, 139.053, 182.015,
184.351, 184.357, 184.359, 184.604, 205.563, 205.979, 210.860, 233.510, 247.130,
