162 payment by credit card which exceeds the fee or surcharge charged by the credit card bank,
163 processor, or issuer for its service. A county or city collector may accept payment by
164 electronic transfers of funds in payment of any tax or license and charge the person making
165 such payment a fee equal to the fee charged the county by the bank, processor, or issuer of
166 such electronic payment.
